window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It's their first night in the hostel and the girls are all set to enjoy it. But not within the four walls of their room. In a new city, where a new life beckons them, they decide to go wild. </p> <p>When the lights are dimmed and the hostel gates closed, Shanaya and her roommates decide to go out clubbing. That's where Shanaya bumps into a lovely stranger, who seems to be drawn to her almost magically. They dance and drink, tease and fulfil, and land up at his flat for the night – no strings attached. </p> <p>Join Shanaya in her adventure with a handsome stranger, who is sure to <i>Remember My Name</i>.</p>"; 
